data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_27","content":"style-guide.md:20:Use one default demo direction only: a simple geometric roof/service mark plus readable RidgeLine Roof Restoration wordmark. Do not create alternate logo options, badges, award seals, or copied reference marks.\nstyle-guide.md:29:- Do not invent reviews, licenses, awards, years in business, street address, or email.\nindex.html:64:    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\nindex.html:65:    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\nindex.html:66:    .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-md); }\nindex.html:67:    .grid-2-1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\nindex.html:68:    .grid-1-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\nindex.html:187:    .hero-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.94fr) minmax(0, 1.06fr); gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: stretch; }\nindex.html:228:      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\nindex.html:248:      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;\nindex.html:258:    .materials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-md); }\nindex.html:261:    .step { counter-increment: step; background: var(--surface); padding: 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 58px 1fr; gap: var(--gap-md); }\nindex.html:278:    .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-md); }\nindex.html:293:      .grid-2, .grid-3, .grid-4, .grid-2-1, .grid-1-2, .hero-split, .project-teaser, .materials { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\nindex.html:298:      .service-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\nindex.html:299:      .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\nindex.html:397:          <p class=\"lead\">No review claims, badges, or awards needed. This template focuses on the visible job: inspect the roof, explain the options, and make it easy to request a quote.</p>\nindex.html:507:          <p class=\"meta\" style=\"margin: 0;\">No address, email, license, review, or award claims are shown in this demo.</p>\ncompact-one-page.html:44:    .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.86fr; gap: 28px; align-items: center; padding-block: clamp(28px, 8vw, 70px); }\ncompact-one-page.html:52:    .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; }\ncompact-one-page.html:55:    .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr; gap: 28px; align-items: start; }\ncompact-one-page.html:67:      .hero, .split, .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n","isError":false}

